OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,FA national centre aimed at combating
OL,7,Fknife crime was launched on Thursday.
OL,9,FThe Home Office-led initiative aims to
OL,10,Fsupport policing and forms part of the
OL,11,Fgovernment's wider ambition to halve
OL,12,Fknife crime in the next 10 years.
OL,14,FThe National Knife Crime Centre will
OL,15,Fbe led by Commander Stephen Clayman,
OL,16,Fwho has been looking into the issue
OL,17,Ffor the National Police Chiefs'
OL,18,FCouncil (NPCC) since 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
