OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775178189
OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,FIn 2024, Clayman led a report into the
OL,7,Fdangers of knives, which highlighted
OL,8,Fthe threat posed by online sellers and
OL,9,Fsocial media platforms.
OL,11,FPart of the National Knife Crime
OL,12,FCentre remit will be to enforce the
OL,13,Frecommendations of that report, such
OL,14,Fas requiring retailers to refer
OL,15,Fsuspicious or bulk knife sales to
OL,16,Fpolice, and requiring retailers to
OL,17,Fbecome registered or licensed to sell
OL,18,Fknives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
