CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775178189
OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,FIt will also support police by
OL,7,Fidentifying and tackling offenders who
OL,8,Fsell and distribute weapons online,
OL,9,Foften referred to as the 'grey market'.
OL,11,FPolice say these people will often
OL,12,Fpurchase knives in bulk and then
OL,13,Fresell them through social media
OL,14,Fplatforms, increasing the
OL,15,Faccessibility of weapons to
OL,16,Findividuals of all ages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
