OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,FSellers of knives outside the UK are
OL,7,Ftypically not subject to the same
OL,8,Frestrictions and legislation, as
OL,9,Fenforced by the Offensive Weapons Act
OL,10,F2019.
OL,12,FThrough close partnership working with
OL,13,FBorder Force and HM Revenue and
OL,14,FCustoms (HMRC), the centre also aims
OL,15,Fto explore how best to close the
OL,16,Floopholes that allow dangerous knives
OL,17,Fto enter the UK market from abroad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
