OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSpeaking at Tuesday's launch,
OL,12,FCommander Clayman said there was a
OL,13,F"growing recognition that our approach
OL,14,Fto knife crime must evolve with the
OL,15,Frapidly changing methods in which
OL,16,Fknives are acquired and used.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
