OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,F"Knife related crime devastates
OL,7,Ffamilies and communities. It places
OL,8,Fimmense pressure on society, policing
OL,9,Fand criminal justice. But it does not
OL,10,Fhave to be inevitable.
OL,12,F"By combining the findings of the
OL,13,Freview with a coordinated national
OL,14,Fsystem, stronger legislation, improved
OL,15,Fregulation, and earlyintervention
OL,16,Fsupport, we do have a clear path
OL,17,Fforward.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
