PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775178189
OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,F"In launching this centre today, we
OL,7,Fare signalling our collective
OL,8,Fcommitment to a safer future; a
OL,9,Fcommitment to tackling the supply
OL,10,Froutes through which knives are
OL,11,Fpurchased, a commitment to
OL,12,Fstrengthening the systems that protect
OL,13,Fyoung people and a commitment to
OL,14,Fensuring that no family has to endure
OL,15,Fthe unimaginable pain of losing a
OL,16,Floved one to knife violence."
OL,18,FThe National Knife Crime Centre's
OL,19,Flaunch comes against a mixed backdrop
OL,20,Fof statistics.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
