PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775178189
OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,FFor too long, gaps in systems and the
OL,7,Faccessibility of dangerous weapons
OL,8,Fhave put young lives at risk. This
OL,9,Fcentre is an opportunity to bring
OL,10,Fpolicing, government, and communities
OL,11,Ftogether to drive real, lasting
OL,12,Fchange."
OL,14,FIn the wake of Ronan's death, his
OL,15,Ffamily campaigned to bring in Ronan's
OL,16,Flaw, legislation banning the sale and
OL,17,Fimporting of dangerous, ninja swords.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
