PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775178189
OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones said the
OL,7,Flaunch was "a major step forward in
OL,8,Four collective effort to tackle this
OL,9,Fharm".
OL,11,FShe insisted: "By bringing together
OL,12,Fpolicing, government and partners in
OL,13,Fone national centre of expertise, we
OL,14,Fare strengthening our ability to
OL,15,Fdisrupt the illegal supply of knives,
OL,16,Fclose loopholes in online and overseas
OL,17,Fsales, and keep dangerous weapons out
OL,18,Fof the wrong hands.
OL,26,@sD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
