OL,3,CBereaved families welcome launch of
OL,4,Cnational knife crime centre
OL,6,F"This government has set an ambitious
OL,7,Fgoal to halve knife crime over the
OL,8,Fnext decade, and the National Knife
OL,9,FCrime Centre will be central to
OL,10,Fdelivering that mission."
